Teesort Printed Men's Round Neck T-Shirt Price: Rs.300

Let your stylish look be the unique one so that everyone takes a notice of you
column13: just put on this blue printed T-shirt from the house of Teesort. Crafted from 100 per cent cotton
column14: this regular fit T-shirt will keep you at comfort all day long. Moreover
column15: this tee comes with a ribbed round neck and half sleeves
column16:
and also has a khadi print in the front that ups the style quotient of the wearer.

\r\n

\r\n\tPut on this Teesort Printed T-shirt with a pair of well-fitted jeans and sneakers. To complete your look just drape a muffler around your neck and carry a canvas sling bag.\xa0Teesort
column18: designs tees that boast of a splash of colours. Outright prints or intricate user-submitted artwork
column19:
all find their place in the fashion aficionados’ wardrobe.

Fabric Care

Machine wash this T-shirt and tumble dry at low temperature. Use medium heat iron on the tee for a crisp look.
